data.title: List of books by author Edgar Rice Burroughs
data.meta_description: Get your Edgar Rice Burroughs books today! Pango Books has a huge selection of new and used titles to choose from. See all books including: Tarzan's Quest, Tarzan of the Apes, Tanar of Pellucidar, Carson of Venus, Collected John Carter of Mars the (Thuvia, Maid of Mars; the Chessmen of Mars; the Master Mind of Mars; a Fighting Man of Mars), John Carter: the Movie Novelization, Fighting Man of Mars, Tarzan of the Apes, Thuvia, Maid of Mars, Tarzan Super Pack, The Collected John Carter of Mars (a Princess of Mars, Gods of Mars, and Warlord of Mars), Classic Tales of Science Fiction and Fantasy, Tarzan at the Earth's Core
